text: Floc can refer to: * Farm Labor Organizing Committee, a labor union * Federated Logic Conference * Flag Letter Of Commendation, U.S. Navy * Flake of precipitate that comes out of solution during the process of flocculation * Floc de Gascogne, a sweet apéritif made from a blend of grape juice and Armagnac * Floc (or Flock), the product of Flocculation * Floc (biofilm), a specialized biofilm suspended in water
title: Floc
